    "Our simple model design using QLoRA works well even with a higher number of parameters.",
    "The data also shows that FLAN T5 outperforms T5, suggesting that the AM task benefits from instruction-tuning on other tasks using FLAN (Wei et al., 2022).",
    "Additionally, we display the AbstRCT and CDCP results in Tables 5 and 6, respectively.",
    "Our FLAN T5-XXL obtained state-of-the-art performance for AbstRCT, with a Relation-F1 score of 47.66 and a Component-F1 score of 72.86.",
    "With Component-F1 and Relation-F1 scores of 72.68 and 33.96, respectively, the CDCP findings likewise show stateof-the-art performance."
